      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.Item.Dysu4F8licjEb2FY]{Vanguard Discipline}</p>\n<p>Your have total control over the entropy embedded in your body and are able to shape it into other forms. As a standard action, you can spend 3 Entropy Points to use @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.spells.Item.gNgdSyi4pXQmasmc]{Polymorph} as a spell-like ability on yourself. Your caster level for this ability is equal to your character level, and the DC is equal to 13 + your Constitution modifier ([[13 + @abilities.con.mod]]).</p>"
